com.betfair.cougar.client

Class AbstractHttpExecutable<HR>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.betfair.cougar.core.api.client.AbstractClientTransport
      • com.betfair.cougar.client.AbstractHttpExecutable<HR>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Executable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AsyncHttpExecutable, HttpClientExecutable

    @ManagedResource
public abstract class AbstractHttpExecutable<HR>
extends AbstractClientTransport
    Base executable which holds the logic of interacting with Execution Venue. Note this marshals the request and un-marshals the response using the provided Transformable
